OL,3,CFuneral for boy, 14, who died in
OL,4,Cindustrial park fire
OL,6,FThe funeral has taken place for the
OL,7,Fteenager who died in a fire near an
OL,8,Findustrial park.
OL,10,FLayton Carr, 14, was found dead inside
OL,11,Fof a building near the Fairfield
OL,12,Findustrial park, in the Bill Quay area
OL,13,Fof Gateshead, on 2 May.
OL,15,FFriends and family gathered together
OL,16,Fto mark Layton's life in a service in
OL,17,FSouth Shields on 14 June.
OL,19,FThe service started at South Shields
OL,20,FCrematorium, followed by the burial at
OL,21,FHarton Cemetery.
