OL,4,Cindustrial park fire
OL,6,FAround two hundred motorbikes,
OL,7,Fdirtbikes and quadbikes were in
OL,8,Fattendance, to pay tribute to Layton,
OL,9,Fwho was passionate about bikes.
OL,11,FDuring the service, a humanist
OL,12,Fcelebrant spoke of Layton and shared
OL,13,Ftributes and memories from his family.
OL,15,FShe said: "He had an awful lot of love
OL,16,Fto give and he has touched so many
OL,17,Flives. He was a proper 'cheeky
OL,18,Fchappie'."
