OL,4,Cindustrial park fire
OL,6,FMourners heard the celebrant retell
OL,7,Fmoving memories from his parents,
OL,8,Fincluding how he loved to help look
OL,9,Fafter younger siblings and was his
OL,10,Fnana's "little helper". Sharing her
OL,11,Fwords, the celebrant said: "Nothing
OL,12,Fwas ever too much trouble for him.".
OL,14,FTributes from close friends were also
OL,15,Fread out, including one which
OL,16,Fdescribed Layton as "the most positive
OL,17,Fperson I have ever known".
