OL,3,CFuneral for boy, 14, who died in
OL,4,Cindustrial park fire
OL,6,FMusical numbers from Gotye and 5ive
OL,7,Fwere played, while the celebrant added
OL,8,Fa further tribute from Layton's
OL,9,Ffamily, saying: "His unforgettable
OL,10,Fspirit will be missed every single
OL,11,Fday."
OL,13,FWritten tributes, including from close
OL,14,Ffamily, adorned flowers. One said:
OL,15,F"You're gone but will never be
OL,16,Fforgotten. Forever in my heart."
OL,18,FDonations were collected in aid of the
OL,19,FTyne and Wear Fire and Rescue Service,
OL,20,Fwho were thanked by Layton's family.
