OL,6,FNorthumbria Police have since arrested
OL,7,F26 children, all aged between 11 and
OL,8,F14, on suspicion of manslaughter.
OL,10,FThey all remain on bail as the
OL,11,Finvestigation into the incident
OL,12,Fcontinues.
